{"id": 1786, "genre": 1000, "title": "在线上听歌，你到底是啥样的？", "description": "关于日常听音乐，你有哪些微妙的习惯？欢迎在评论区补充啊。（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 20560, "comment_count": 114, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201707051307592fOlTCpPuWi6YrQg.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-07-13T17:00:15Z", "questions": [{"id": 2566, "title": "在线上听歌，你到底是啥样的？", "content": "使用音乐播放器的时候，你是哪一型人？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 219466, "content": "大部分时间都用一个固定的播放器，有啥听啥", "image": "img/option/option/20170705165514kwE6K9cXL5UiIr72.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 219468, "content": "常用播放器至少三个，方能容纳我兼容并包的流派喜好", "image": "img/option/option/20170705165919g1ZAMVWCxKY3Evow.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 219471, "content": "会把自己听到的鬼畜 or 好听歌曲分享给好友", "image": "img/option/option/20170705170737qQJwpmCOFSNZ7ce9.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 219488, "content": "经常看歌曲评论区，有时候还会参与讨论或者点赞", "image": "img/option/option/20170705172405oiCNz5B2hprdDIe4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 219489, "content": "当背景音的时候也要让屏幕亮着，随时看看歌名或者歌词", "image": "img/option/option/20170705172737ghWpNJvSwbQoRcE1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 219495, "content": "关注一些好的歌单，或者自己制作歌单", "image": "img/option/option/20170706134841rewOkfXlVzs5bK8B.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 219497, "content": "不怎么听完整专辑，只听猜你喜欢或者自己收藏的歌", "image": "img/option/option/20170706135954KyA8Snk3INYLstMB.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 219501, "content": "早上打开当日推荐，删掉不喜欢的，开始循环上一整天", "image": "img/option/option/20170706140312NzkL8TI6ycopl9GO.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 219502, "content": "收藏了很多歌手和专辑，并精心分类", "image": "img/option/option/20170706135839UN3LIEqzTiAgy21Y.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 219512, "content": "经常使用“识别歌曲”功能随时存下自己喜欢的歌", "image": "img/option/option/20170705180508QxKaEu6WXmkdCA1Y.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}